{"video_id": "cI9M9k-V0ic", "title": "Planet of Immortals | Bhagavad Gita Chapter 8 Verse 20 - 22 | HG Amitasana Das | HKM Mumbai", "speaker": "HG Amitasana Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cI9M9k-V0ic", "duration": 1440, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 26.0, "text": " So, today the topic is Planet of the Immortals, based on the teachings of His Divine Grace"}, {"start": 26.0, "end": 28.22, "text": " A.C. Bhaktivedanta Swamishlaprabhupada."}, {"start": 29.72, "end": 33.2, "text": " So, let's chant this verse together. This is the 20th verse from the 8th chapter."}, {"start": 54.2, "end": 55.8, "text": " So, here in this verse,"}, {"start": 55.800000000000004, "end": 62.00000000000001, "text": " Krishna is saying, this particular world which we are part of, which is the material world,"}, {"start": 64.72, "end": 76.08000000000001, "text": " it is vyakto avyakta. Vyakto means? Vyakta. Vyakthona. It is manifest. And avyakta means?"}, {"start": 77.30000000000001, "end": 85.0, "text": " Unmanifest. So, it comes into being and at one point it gets annihilated. In that sense, this"}, {"start": 85.8, "end": 99.96, "text": " is temporary. We see everything in this world is temporary, including our bodies. So, then"}, {"start": 99.96, "end": 107.53999999999999, "text": " Krishna is saying, parastasmatubhavinu, beyond this material world, beyond this material creation,"}, {"start": 107.53999999999999, "end": 113.82, "text": " there is another world. And which is that world?"}, {"start": 115.8, "end": 125.14, "text": " It is the spiritual world, which has many, many Vaikuntha planets and the topmost of which is Goloka Vrindavan."}, {"start": 126.02, "end": 130.18, "text": " So, elaborate description of this spiritual planet, the spiritual world is given in our scriptures."}, {"start": 130.32, "end": 135.84, "text": " In fact, all the scriptures of the world in different religions, they call it by different names."}, {"start": 135.96, "end": 142.28, "text": " Somebody call it heaven, jannat, you know, so many other names are there, which are synonyms in that sense."}, {"start": 142.28, "end": 145.57999999999998, "text": " So, Krishna is saying, beyond this material world, there is another world."}, {"start": 145.57999999999998, "end": 145.78, "text": " So, Krishna is saying, beyond this material world, beyond this material world, beyond this material world, there is another world."}, {"start": 145.8, "end": 153.04000000000002, "text": " material world which is vyakta and avyakta, there is another world, and that world, the"}, {"start": 153.04000000000002, "end": 155.12, "text": " nature of that world is sanatana."}, {"start": 155.12, "end": 160.3, "text": " Sanatana means eternal, does not cease to be."}, {"start": 160.3, "end": 167.0, "text": " Yasa sarve bhuteshu and those who go there, yet there is another nature which is eternal"}, {"start": 167.0, "end": 172.56, "text": " and is transcendental to this manifested and unmanifested matter."}, {"start": 172.56, "end": 176.46, "text": " It is supreme and is never annihilated."}, {"start": 176.46, "end": 182.42000000000002, "text": " When all in this world is annihilated, that part remains as it is."}, {"start": 182.42000000000002, "end": 191.5, "text": " We all are looking for permanence because we are part of that world."}, {"start": 191.5, "end": 195.68, "text": " As spirit soul we are eternal and that world is eternal."}, {"start": 195.68, "end": 202.24, "text": " And we are put in a material body which is temporary in a world which is temporary."}, {"start": 202.24, "end": 204.48000000000002, "text": " And hence there is a struggle."}, {"start": 204.48000000000002, "end": 211.92000000000002, "text": " It is like a fish out of its natural habitat which is water, when put on land, irrespective"}, {"start": 211.92000000000002, "end": 215.48000000000002, "text": " of how much comfort we give to the fish, it will wriggle out."}, {"start": 215.48000000000002, "end": 220.52, "text": " Because that is not its natural habitat."}, {"start": 220.52, "end": 222.38, "text": " Fish out of water."}, {"start": 222.38, "end": 228.08, "text": " You put the fish back in water, it is back in its natural state."}, {"start": 228.08, "end": 230.14000000000001, "text": " So we right now are inhabiting a material body."}, {"start": 230.14000000000001, "end": 231.14000000000001, "text": " We are living in a material body."}, {"start": 231.14000000000001, "end": 232.14000000000001, "text": " We are living in a material body."}, {"start": 232.14000000000001, "end": 234.48000000000002, "text": " We are living in a material body."}, {"start": 234.48000000000002, "end": 241.76000000000002, "text": " And this material body is going through transformation, janma, mrityu, jarav, yadi."}, {"start": 241.76000000000002, "end": 246.76000000000002, "text": " It comes into being one day, we take birth and then much against our wish we encounter"}, {"start": 246.76000000000002, "end": 249.60000000000002, "text": " different kinds of diseases."}, {"start": 249.60000000000002, "end": 258.58000000000004, "text": " And then it decays, deteriorates with time and then one fine day we die."}, {"start": 258.58000000000004, "end": 259.58000000000004, "text": " Do we die?"}, {"start": 259.58000000000004, "end": 260.58000000000004, "text": " Yes?"}, {"start": 260.58000000000004, "end": 261.58000000000004, "text": " No?"}, {"start": 261.58, "end": 262.58, "text": " No?"}, {"start": 262.58, "end": 263.58, "text": " The body dies."}, {"start": 263.58, "end": 264.58, "text": " The body dies."}, {"start": 264.58, "end": 270.2, "text": " But we have identified ourselves with the body, we experience death."}, {"start": 270.2, "end": 272.71999999999997, "text": " And then again the next cycle begins."}, {"start": 272.71999999999997, "end": 276.58, "text": " And this is going on over many many lifetimes."}, {"start": 276.58, "end": 284.94, "text": " And this cycle is called punarapi janma, punarapi marana."}, {"start": 284.94, "end": 288.58, "text": " So that world is transcendental."}, {"start": 288.58, "end": 289.58, "text": " What is the meaning of transcendental?"}, {"start": 289.58, "end": 290.58, "text": " Transcendental."}, {"start": 290.58, "end": 291.58, "text": " Transcendental."}, {"start": 291.58, "end": 292.58, "text": " What does the meaning of transcendental mean?"}, {"start": 292.58, "end": 293.58, "text": " What is the meaning of transcendental?"}, {"start": 293.58, "end": 294.58, "text": " Transcendental."}, {"start": 294.58, "end": 295.58, "text": " Transcendental."}, {"start": 295.58, "end": 306.02, "text": " The word transcend means which is beyond, which surpasses, which is out of the limit"}, {"start": 306.02, "end": 309.88, "text": " of the material domain and eternal."}, {"start": 309.88, "end": 312.44, "text": " It is never annihilated."}, {"start": 312.44, "end": 317.58, "text": " And it is opposite in quality to the material nature."}, {"start": 317.58, "end": 320.58, "text": " It is full of sat, chit and?"}, {"start": 320.58, "end": 321.58, "text": " Ananda."}, {"start": 321.58, "end": 322.58, "text": " Ananda."}, {"start": 322.58, "end": 335.82, "text": " Sat means it is eternal, chit means there is no ignorance and ananda is full of bliss."}, {"start": 335.82, "end": 342.41999999999996, "text": " As spirit souls we also have that natural intrinsic quality."}, {"start": 342.41999999999996, "end": 348.58, "text": " But right now because we are covered by this material body, that quality is extinguished."}, {"start": 348.58, "end": 349.58, "text": " Right?"}, {"start": 349.58, "end": 356.94, "text": " So I gave you example of fish out of water."}, {"start": 356.94, "end": 361.62, "text": " So Krishna is inviting us to that world."}, {"start": 361.62, "end": 363.74, "text": " Let me give you a very good example."}, {"start": 363.74, "end": 369.82, "text": " Let's say a person is walking up the hill and that hill has lot of thorns, lot of pebbles,"}, {"start": 369.82, "end": 377.46, "text": " lot of small pieces of stones with sharp edges."}, {"start": 377.46, "end": 378.58, "text": " And the person is walking barefoot."}, {"start": 378.58, "end": 387.62, "text": " Now as soon as he is climbing the hill, suddenly a thorn pricks his leg and he feels lot of pain"}, {"start": 387.62, "end": 390.47999999999996, "text": " and blood starts oozing out."}, {"start": 390.47999999999996, "end": 392.94, "text": " Now you are by his side, what will you do?"}, {"start": 392.94, "end": 397.96, "text": " You will help him with some first aid, remove the thorn."}, {"start": 397.96, "end": 403.26, "text": " And then wish him good luck, wish him good health, get well soon and then again the person"}, {"start": 403.26, "end": 406.21999999999997, "text": " starts walking up the hill."}, {"start": 406.21999999999997, "end": 407.58, "text": " Because that hill has lot of thorns."}, {"start": 407.58, "end": 412.03999999999996, "text": " And he is walking barefoot and there are lot of sharp stones there."}, {"start": 412.03999999999996, "end": 414.0, "text": " Again he will get pricked with a thorn."}, {"start": 414.0, "end": 419.4, "text": " And again you rush him to give a first aid."}, {"start": 419.4, "end": 424.62, "text": " Should we give him first aid, yes or no?"}, {"start": 424.62, "end": 430.7, "text": " Apart from giving first aid, what should we do?"}, {"start": 430.7, "end": 431.7, "text": " Because this will go on."}, {"start": 431.7, "end": 434.58, "text": " How long you can keep giving first aid?"}, {"start": 434.58, "end": 437.38, "text": " Next moment again he will get pricked with a thorn."}, {"start": 437.38, "end": 445.24, "text": " So while you give him a first aid, you should also try to find is there another way which"}, {"start": 445.24, "end": 450.0, "text": " is free of thorns, another path which he can tread which is free of thorns where he can"}, {"start": 450.0, "end": 455.78, "text": " go to the destination or you can give him slippers."}, {"start": 455.78, "end": 457.84, "text": " Just giving first aid is not the solution."}, {"start": 457.84, "end": 464.38, "text": " Right now in the material world, all the solutions what we are trying to get is like a first aid."}, {"start": 464.38, "end": 465.38, "text": " Intrinsically."}, {"start": 465.38, "end": 466.38, "text": " Intrinsically."}, {"start": 466.38, "end": 467.38, "text": " Intrinsically."}, {"start": 467.38, "end": 468.38, "text": " Intrinsically."}, {"start": 468.38, "end": 469.38, "text": " Now..."}, {"start": 469.38, "end": 470.38, "text": " And then we have to stop doing it from the next moment."}, {"start": 470.38, "end": 497.14, "text": " Lot of"}, {"start": 497.38, "end": 498.28, "text": " come to that world."}, {"start": 500.52, "end": 501.36, "text": " This is not"}, {"start": 501.36, "end": 503.32, "text": " the world where we will experience that peace"}, {"start": 503.32, "end": 505.4, "text": " and happiness which we are hankering to experience."}, {"start": 507.21999999999997, "end": 509.34, "text": " And while we are in this material world,"}, {"start": 509.42, "end": 511.36, "text": " we are not pessimistic. We can wear slippers."}, {"start": 511.65999999999997, "end": 513.28, "text": " What is the wearing of slippers equivalent to?"}, {"start": 517.76, "end": 519.28, "text": " To take shelter of the Lord."}, {"start": 520.88, "end": 522.9, "text": " To have consciousness of God."}, {"start": 522.9, "end": 524.9, "text": " To have dependence on God."}, {"start": 527.38, "end": 530.9399999999999, "text": " Learn to tolerate."}, {"start": 531.42, "end": 532.38, "text": " Remembering the Lord."}, {"start": 538.4, "end": 539.58, "text": " Text 21."}, {"start": 540.26, "end": 541.76, "text": " That supreme abode is called"}, {"start": 541.76, "end": 544.46, "text": " unmanifested and infallible."}, {"start": 545.72, "end": 547.58, "text": " And it is a supreme destination."}, {"start": 548.4, "end": 549.76, "text": " We all have some goals,"}, {"start": 549.9399999999999, "end": 552.38, "text": " some aspirations. That's a supreme destination."}, {"start": 552.78, "end": 554.24, "text": " That's a supreme goal."}, {"start": 554.66, "end": 556.18, "text": " That's what we should long for."}, {"start": 557.38, "end": 559.76, "text": " That will give us solution to all the challenges"}, {"start": 559.76, "end": 560.74, "text": " what we are encountering."}, {"start": 560.8, "end": 563.4399999999999, "text": " All other things are frustrated in a thorny place."}, {"start": 564.88, "end": 566.1, "text": " When one goes there,"}, {"start": 566.12, "end": 567.2, "text": " he never comes back."}, {"start": 567.74, "end": 569.32, "text": " That is my supreme abode."}, {"start": 570.68, "end": 571.48, "text": " Now mind you,"}, {"start": 572.24, "end": 573.14, "text": " for us right now,"}, {"start": 573.2, "end": 574.2, "text": " it may appear fictitious."}, {"start": 574.4, "end": 577.28, "text": " It may appear something very fairy tale like."}, {"start": 578.48, "end": 579.5, "text": " But these are the words"}, {"start": 579.5, "end": 580.4, "text": " spoken by the Lord."}, {"start": 582.04, "end": 583.2, "text": " Now a lot of people"}, {"start": 583.2, "end": 584.84, "text": " have heard about this word called"}, {"start": 584.84, "end": 585.34, "text": " moksha."}, {"start": 586.54, "end": 587.36, "text": " So what is moksha?"}, {"start": 587.38, "end": 593.04, "text": " Moksha means liberation."}, {"start": 593.24, "end": 593.58, "text": " Very good."}, {"start": 593.92, "end": 594.66, "text": " What is liberation?"}, {"start": 595.54, "end": 596.06, "text": " Moksha."}, {"start": 597.48, "end": 598.12, "text": " Going cycle."}, {"start": 600.84, "end": 603.7, "text": " This soul which is caught up"}, {"start": 603.7, "end": 605.3, "text": " in the cycle of birth and death"}, {"start": 605.3, "end": 606.8, "text": " in this material world"}, {"start": 606.8, "end": 610.08, "text": " comes out of the cycle of birth and death"}, {"start": 610.08, "end": 611.66, "text": " and goes back to the"}, {"start": 611.66, "end": 612.76, "text": " spiritual world."}, {"start": 616.0, "end": 617.36, "text": " Now what happens in the spiritual world?"}, {"start": 617.36, "end": 619.26, "text": " Does it just merge"}, {"start": 619.26, "end": 621.48, "text": " and you know"}, {"start": 621.48, "end": 623.2, "text": " just exist in some sky"}, {"start": 623.2, "end": 625.12, "text": " as a small"}, {"start": 625.12, "end": 627.14, "text": " spark of light?"}, {"start": 627.26, "end": 627.82, "text": " What happens?"}, {"start": 629.46, "end": 631.28, "text": " That soul is engaged"}, {"start": 631.28, "end": 633.04, "text": " in blissful service of"}, {"start": 633.04, "end": 634.0, "text": " the Lord."}, {"start": 634.88, "end": 637.2, "text": " Right now we are engaged in the service of"}, {"start": 637.2, "end": 638.3000000000001, "text": " false masters."}, {"start": 639.62, "end": 641.22, "text": " Our kama, krodha,"}, {"start": 641.4, "end": 643.24, "text": " mada. Our senses"}, {"start": 643.24, "end": 644.4200000000001, "text": " have become our masters."}, {"start": 644.4200000000001, "end": 646.26, "text": " The body with the senses"}, {"start": 646.26, "end": 647.32, "text": " have become our masters."}, {"start": 647.36, "end": 648.58, "text": " They are dictating us."}, {"start": 648.6800000000001, "end": 650.26, "text": " See this. Eat this. Drink this."}, {"start": 650.76, "end": 651.54, "text": " Touch this."}, {"start": 652.38, "end": 653.36, "text": " And at heavy cost."}, {"start": 656.1800000000001, "end": 659.0, "text": " And when we go back to the spiritual world"}, {"start": 659.0, "end": 660.94, "text": " we engage in blissful service"}, {"start": 660.94, "end": 662.04, "text": " of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 665.38, "end": 666.0600000000001, "text": " And"}, {"start": 666.0600000000001, "end": 668.82, "text": " genuine spirituality involves"}, {"start": 668.82, "end": 670.62, "text": " we try practicing"}, {"start": 670.62, "end": 672.58, "text": " that while we are"}, {"start": 672.58, "end": 673.78, "text": " in this material world."}, {"start": 675.74, "end": 676.6800000000001, "text": " So all the"}, {"start": 676.6800000000001, "end": 677.1800000000001, "text": " devotional services"}, {"start": 677.36, "end": 679.0600000000001, "text": " chanting, hearing,"}, {"start": 679.0600000000001, "end": 681.3000000000001, "text": " paada sevanam, archanam, vandanam,"}, {"start": 681.3000000000001, "end": 683.46, "text": " dasyam, sakhyam, atma nivedanam,"}, {"start": 683.46, "end": 685.14, "text": " all this process of devotional service"}, {"start": 685.14, "end": 686.28, "text": " is like"}, {"start": 686.28, "end": 689.0, "text": " qualifying us"}, {"start": 689.0, "end": 690.92, "text": " to do what we are going to do it in the"}, {"start": 690.92, "end": 692.32, "text": " spiritual world."}, {"start": 694.28, "end": 695.52, "text": " So for a devotee"}, {"start": 695.52, "end": 696.94, "text": " who is engaged, sent person"}, {"start": 696.94, "end": 698.62, "text": " throughout the day in the service of the Lord,"}, {"start": 698.72, "end": 701.14, "text": " in that sense it is not different whether he is in the"}, {"start": 701.14, "end": 702.1800000000001, "text": " material world or"}, {"start": 702.1800000000001, "end": 704.2, "text": " in the spiritual world."}, {"start": 705.1800000000001, "end": 706.94, "text": " See already he is liberated."}, {"start": 707.36, "end": 709.94, "text": " Because what he is going to do in the spiritual world"}, {"start": 709.94, "end": 711.22, "text": " he is doing it here."}, {"start": 711.9, "end": 714.4, "text": " So Krishna is saying while you are in this material world"}, {"start": 714.4, "end": 715.24, "text": " do that."}, {"start": 718.02, "end": 719.64, "text": " And at the end of the life"}, {"start": 719.64, "end": 720.98, "text": " you will get qualified to"}, {"start": 720.98, "end": 722.98, "text": " go back to the spiritual world."}, {"start": 724.5, "end": 725.86, "text": " And what is that dhama?"}, {"start": 726.08, "end": 727.26, "text": " It's chintamani dhama."}, {"start": 727.44, "end": 729.88, "text": " Place where all desires get fulfilled."}, {"start": 731.88, "end": 734.44, "text": " Right now we have so many unfulfilled desires."}, {"start": 734.94, "end": 736.22, "text": " Lust, greed."}, {"start": 736.22, "end": 737.28, "text": " You know because"}, {"start": 737.36, "end": 738.2, "text": " we are not complete."}, {"start": 738.98, "end": 740.6, "text": " We are not experiencing that happiness."}, {"start": 740.82, "end": 741.96, "text": " So we are having some hope."}, {"start": 742.1800000000001, "end": 744.52, "text": " If I achieve this, if I get this, if I have this"}, {"start": 744.52, "end": 745.4, "text": " I will be happy."}, {"start": 745.9, "end": 747.78, "text": " There we are completely satisfied."}, {"start": 747.94, "end": 749.08, "text": " Completely contented."}, {"start": 750.48, "end": 752.36, "text": " And the trees, their example is given"}, {"start": 752.36, "end": 754.46, "text": " in Brahma Samhita by Lord Brahma"}, {"start": 754.46, "end": 756.46, "text": " in our authorized Vedic literatures."}, {"start": 756.62, "end": 758.14, "text": " The trees are like desired trees."}, {"start": 760.26, "end": 762.1800000000001, "text": " And the cows are like surabhi cows."}, {"start": 762.28, "end": 764.26, "text": " Surabhi cows means they can give unlimited"}, {"start": 764.26, "end": 765.9200000000001, "text": " profuse supply of milk."}, {"start": 765.9200000000001, "end": 766.4, "text": " Cow."}, {"start": 767.36, "end": 769.36, "text": " And everything is full of spiritual bliss."}, {"start": 769.36, "end": 771.36, "text": " A vivid description of this is given in the Brahma Samhita."}, {"start": 771.36, "end": 773.36, "text": " Prayers offered by Lord Brahma to Lord Krishna."}, {"start": 773.36, "end": 775.36, "text": " When one attains to it,"}, {"start": 775.36, "end": 777.36, "text": " he never returns to this material world."}, {"start": 777.36, "end": 779.36, "text": " Krishna says,"}, {"start": 779.36, "end": 781.36, "text": " yad gatva na nivartante tad dhamam paramam mama."}, {"start": 781.36, "end": 783.36, "text": " And Krishna also says,"}, {"start": 783.36, "end": 785.36, "text": " yamyam vapi smaran bhavam kyajtyante kalevaram."}, {"start": 785.36, "end": 787.36, "text": " If we are able to remember the Lord"}, {"start": 787.36, "end": 789.36, "text": " while we quit our body,"}, {"start": 789.36, "end": 791.36, "text": " we get qualified to go back"}, {"start": 791.36, "end": 793.36, "text": " to the spiritual world."}, {"start": 793.36, "end": 795.36, "text": " And this is what we are doing."}, {"start": 795.36, "end": 796.86, "text": " And this is what we are doing."}, {"start": 796.86, "end": 798.86, "text": " We are qualified to reach back"}, {"start": 798.86, "end": 800.86, "text": " to the eternal abode."}, {"start": 800.86, "end": 802.86, "text": " If we have unfulfilled desires"}, {"start": 802.86, "end": 804.86, "text": " and we have attachment to things"}, {"start": 804.86, "end": 806.86, "text": " based on that we die,"}, {"start": 806.86, "end": 808.86, "text": " to fulfill those desires,"}, {"start": 808.86, "end": 810.86, "text": " we get appropriate material body."}, {"start": 810.86, "end": 812.86, "text": " Then punarapi janma punarapi maran."}, {"start": 814.86, "end": 816.86, "text": " Text 22."}, {"start": 816.86, "end": 818.86, "text": " The supreme personality of Godhead"}, {"start": 818.86, "end": 820.86, "text": " who is greater than all"}, {"start": 820.86, "end": 822.86, "text": " is attainable by unalloyed devotion."}, {"start": 822.86, "end": 824.86, "text": " Now here Krishna himself is saying,"}, {"start": 824.86, "end": 826.86, "text": " the supreme personality of Godhead"}, {"start": 826.86, "end": 828.86, "text": " who is greater than all"}, {"start": 828.86, "end": 830.86, "text": " is attainable."}, {"start": 830.86, "end": 832.86, "text": " How do we attain supreme Lord?"}, {"start": 832.86, "end": 834.86, "text": " How do we attain that eternal abode?"}, {"start": 834.86, "end": 836.86, "text": " By unalloyed devotion."}, {"start": 836.86, "end": 838.86, "text": " Bhaktyas labhyas cha ananya."}, {"start": 838.86, "end": 840.86, "text": " Bhaktyas labhyas cha ananya."}, {"start": 840.86, "end": 842.86, "text": " Ananya means"}, {"start": 842.86, "end": 844.86, "text": " ananya bhakti,"}, {"start": 844.86, "end": 846.86, "text": " undivided,"}, {"start": 846.86, "end": 848.86, "text": " unalloyed,"}, {"start": 848.86, "end": 850.86, "text": " not mixed."}, {"start": 850.86, "end": 852.86, "text": " Alloy you understand?"}, {"start": 852.86, "end": 854.86, "text": " Alloy of some metals."}, {"start": 854.86, "end": 856.86, "text": " Unalloyed devotion."}, {"start": 856.86, "end": 858.86, "text": " Ananyas bhaktyas labhyas."}, {"start": 858.86, "end": 860.86, "text": " Labhyas means to achieve."}, {"start": 860.86, "end": 862.86, "text": " Purushaata para."}, {"start": 862.86, "end": 864.86, "text": " Para means that Purusha,"}, {"start": 864.86, "end": 866.86, "text": " that supreme personality of Godhead,"}, {"start": 866.86, "end": 868.86, "text": " that supreme abode."}, {"start": 868.86, "end": 870.86, "text": " Partha bhaktyas labhyas to ananya."}, {"start": 870.86, "end": 872.86, "text": " Ananya."}, {"start": 872.86, "end": 874.86, "text": " Although he is present in his abode,"}, {"start": 874.86, "end": 876.86, "text": " he is all pervading"}, {"start": 876.86, "end": 878.86, "text": " and everything is situated within him."}, {"start": 878.86, "end": 880.86, "text": " Although he is in his abode,"}, {"start": 880.86, "end": 882.86, "text": " he is in Vaikuntha."}, {"start": 882.86, "end": 884.86, "text": " He is in Vaikuntha."}, {"start": 884.86, "end": 886.86, "text": " He is in Goloka Vrindavan."}, {"start": 886.86, "end": 888.86, "text": " Still he is manifested everywhere"}, {"start": 888.86, "end": 890.86, "text": " in the material and"}, {"start": 890.86, "end": 892.86, "text": " spiritual creation."}, {"start": 892.86, "end": 894.86, "text": " And everything is situated"}, {"start": 894.86, "end": 896.86, "text": " within him."}, {"start": 896.86, "end": 898.86, "text": " So we talked about how we can attain him."}, {"start": 898.86, "end": 900.86, "text": " How we can achieve that supreme abode."}, {"start": 900.86, "end": 902.86, "text": " Only by bhakti or devotion"}, {"start": 902.86, "end": 904.86, "text": " service can one enter into"}, {"start": 904.86, "end": 906.86, "text": " Vaikuntha spiritual planetary system."}, {"start": 906.86, "end": 908.86, "text": " Have you heard of this?"}, {"start": 908.86, "end": 910.86, "text": " When somebody dies we have Vaikuntha Samaradhanay."}, {"start": 910.86, "end": 912.86, "text": " Have you heard of this?"}, {"start": 912.86, "end": 914.86, "text": " So basically the prayers are being offered"}, {"start": 914.86, "end": 916.86, "text": " that the person, that soul"}, {"start": 916.86, "end": 918.86, "text": " which have left the body enters"}, {"start": 918.86, "end": 920.86, "text": " Vaikuntha."}, {"start": 922.86, "end": 924.86, "text": " And what is the meaning of Vaikuntha?"}, {"start": 928.86, "end": 930.86, "text": " Kuntha means"}, {"start": 930.86, "end": 932.86, "text": " Sanskrit word Kuntha means"}, {"start": 932.86, "end": 934.86, "text": " anxiety."}, {"start": 934.86, "end": 936.86, "text": " Vaikuntha means a place where there is"}, {"start": 936.86, "end": 938.86, "text": " no anxiety."}, {"start": 938.86, "end": 940.86, "text": " No financial problems."}, {"start": 940.86, "end": 942.86, "text": " No financial problems."}, {"start": 942.86, "end": 944.86, "text": " No EMI's."}, {"start": 944.86, "end": 946.86, "text": " No EMI's."}, {"start": 946.86, "end": 948.86, "text": " What else?"}, {"start": 948.86, "end": 950.86, "text": " What else?"}, {"start": 950.86, "end": 952.86, "text": " What else is not there?"}, {"start": 952.86, "end": 954.86, "text": " No?"}, {"start": 954.86, "end": 956.86, "text": " No exams."}, {"start": 956.86, "end": 958.86, "text": " No exams. Yes."}, {"start": 958.86, "end": 960.86, "text": " What else?"}, {"start": 960.86, "end": 962.86, "text": " Let's count some of the things"}, {"start": 962.86, "end": 964.86, "text": " which bothers us."}, {"start": 964.86, "end": 966.86, "text": " No diseases."}, {"start": 966.86, "end": 968.86, "text": " No diseases. Yes."}, {"start": 968.86, "end": 970.86, "text": " What else?"}, {"start": 970.86, "end": 972.86, "text": " What else?"}, {"start": 972.86, "end": 974.86, "text": " Okay."}, {"start": 974.86, "end": 976.86, "text": " So one time Prabhupada"}, {"start": 976.86, "end": 978.86, "text": " shares a very interesting story."}, {"start": 978.86, "end": 980.86, "text": " He says when Jesus"}, {"start": 980.86, "end": 982.86, "text": " was trying to preach"}, {"start": 982.86, "end": 984.86, "text": " you know. So he"}, {"start": 984.86, "end": 986.86, "text": " not Jesus. Some Christian"}, {"start": 986.86, "end": 988.86, "text": " preachers, they were trying to preach"}, {"start": 988.86, "end": 990.86, "text": " and they went to a place where"}, {"start": 990.86, "end": 992.86, "text": " there were coal mines."}, {"start": 992.86, "end": 994.86, "text": " So they were trying to say that"}, {"start": 994.86, "end": 996.86, "text": " if you sin you will go to hell."}, {"start": 996.86, "end": 1000.86, "text": " So"}, {"start": 1000.86, "end": 1002.86, "text": " now he says how does it"}, {"start": 1002.86, "end": 1004.86, "text": " matter? By the way"}, {"start": 1004.86, "end": 1006.86, "text": " what is hell?"}, {"start": 1006.86, "end": 1008.86, "text": " So he says it is dark."}, {"start": 1008.86, "end": 1010.86, "text": " It's damp."}, {"start": 1010.86, "end": 1012.86, "text": " And the coal"}, {"start": 1012.86, "end": 1014.86, "text": " miner says how different it is from"}, {"start": 1014.86, "end": 1016.86, "text": " our work place."}, {"start": 1016.86, "end": 1018.86, "text": " So why we have to worry"}, {"start": 1018.86, "end": 1020.86, "text": " about going to hell? We are perfectly fine."}, {"start": 1020.86, "end": 1022.86, "text": " We are okay with it."}, {"start": 1022.86, "end": 1024.8600000000001, "text": " So then he says"}, {"start": 1024.8600000000001, "end": 1026.8600000000001, "text": " there is no newspapers there."}, {"start": 1026.8600000000001, "end": 1028.8600000000001, "text": " And then immediately"}, {"start": 1028.8600000000001, "end": 1030.8600000000001, "text": " no, no, no."}, {"start": 1030.8600000000001, "end": 1032.8600000000001, "text": " Then it's a hell."}, {"start": 1032.8600000000001, "end": 1034.8600000000001, "text": " So we all have a definition"}, {"start": 1034.8600000000001, "end": 1036.8600000000001, "text": " of what is good, what is bad."}, {"start": 1036.8600000000001, "end": 1038.8600000000001, "text": " So Krishna dwelling in Goloka Vrindavan"}, {"start": 1038.8600000000001, "end": 1040.8600000000001, "text": " his supreme abode systematically"}, {"start": 1040.8600000000001, "end": 1042.8600000000001, "text": " conducts all affairs of both universes"}, {"start": 1042.8600000000001, "end": 1044.8600000000001, "text": " material and spiritual."}, {"start": 1044.8600000000001, "end": 1046.8600000000001, "text": " So we will stop here."}, {"start": 1046.8600000000001, "end": 1048.8600000000001, "text": " Anyone has any question, anything like to ask"}, {"start": 1048.8600000000001, "end": 1050.8600000000001, "text": " and then we move on to the discussion"}, {"start": 1050.8600000000001, "end": 1052.8600000000001, "text": " on chanting."}, {"start": 1052.8600000000001, "end": 1054.8600000000001, "text": " Any questions on"}, {"start": 1054.8600000000001, "end": 1056.8600000000001, "text": " what we discussed?"}, {"start": 1056.8600000000001, "end": 1062.8600000000001, "text": " So what Gita is trying to do"}, {"start": 1062.8600000000001, "end": 1064.8600000000001, "text": " is yes we are so"}, {"start": 1064.8600000000001, "end": 1066.8600000000001, "text": " so obsessed with our"}, {"start": 1066.8600000000001, "end": 1068.8600000000001, "text": " day to day life."}, {"start": 1068.8600000000001, "end": 1070.8600000000001, "text": " It's like a rat race."}, {"start": 1070.8600000000001, "end": 1072.8600000000001, "text": " Morning we get up and then"}, {"start": 1072.8600000000001, "end": 1074.8600000000001, "text": " we have our own things to catch up with"}, {"start": 1074.8600000000001, "end": 1076.8600000000001, "text": " our responsibilities, this thing"}, {"start": 1076.8600000000001, "end": 1078.8600000000001, "text": " and we have forgotten the overall picture."}, {"start": 1080.8600000000001, "end": 1082.8600000000001, "text": " What is that overall picture?"}, {"start": 1082.8600000000001, "end": 1084.8600000000001, "text": " We are that spirit soul."}, {"start": 1084.8600000000001, "end": 1086.8600000000001, "text": " That soul is eternal."}, {"start": 1086.8600000000001, "end": 1088.8600000000001, "text": " This life is a small phase"}, {"start": 1088.8600000000001, "end": 1090.8600000000001, "text": " in our eternal existence."}, {"start": 1092.8600000000001, "end": 1094.8600000000001, "text": " It's a small phase."}, {"start": 1094.8600000000001, "end": 1096.8600000000001, "text": " And especially"}, {"start": 1096.8600000000001, "end": 1098.8600000000001, "text": " because we have got human birth"}, {"start": 1098.8600000000001, "end": 1100.8600000000001, "text": " in this life, it is a very very"}, {"start": 1100.8600000000001, "end": 1102.8600000000001, "text": " important responsibility that"}, {"start": 1102.8600000000001, "end": 1104.8600000000001, "text": " in this life because of our developed intelligence"}, {"start": 1104.8600000000001, "end": 1106.8600000000001, "text": " we can inquire into"}, {"start": 1106.8600000000001, "end": 1108.8600000000001, "text": " Who am I?"}, {"start": 1108.8600000000001, "end": 1110.8600000000001, "text": " What is the purpose of my life?"}, {"start": 1112.8600000000001, "end": 1114.8600000000001, "text": " What happens to me"}, {"start": 1114.8600000000001, "end": 1116.8600000000001, "text": " after death?"}, {"start": 1116.8600000000001, "end": 1118.8600000000001, "text": " Why am I suffering?"}, {"start": 1118.8600000000001, "end": 1120.8600000000001, "text": " Why am I suffering?"}, {"start": 1122.8600000000001, "end": 1124.8600000000001, "text": " If we don't ask these fundamental"}, {"start": 1124.8600000000001, "end": 1126.8600000000001, "text": " questions as scriptures say"}, {"start": 1126.8600000000001, "end": 1128.8600000000001, "text": " we are not doing justice to the human birth."}, {"start": 1130.8600000000001, "end": 1132.8600000000001, "text": " We are busy doing first aid treatment"}, {"start": 1132.8600000000001, "end": 1134.8600000000001, "text": " without knowing the real problem."}, {"start": 1134.8600000000001, "end": 1136.8600000000001, "text": " Krishna says"}, {"start": 1136.8600000000001, "end": 1138.8600000000001, "text": " Janma Mrityu Jara Vyadi"}, {"start": 1138.8600000000001, "end": 1140.8600000000001, "text": " Dukha Doshanu Darshanam Anukan"}, {"start": 1140.8600000000001, "end": 1142.8600000000001, "text": " Perceive that Janma Mrityu Jara Vyadi"}, {"start": 1142.8600000000001, "end": 1144.8600000000001, "text": " These are the real challenges for which"}, {"start": 1144.8600000000001, "end": 1146.8600000000001, "text": " he is in knowledge."}, {"start": 1148.8600000000001, "end": 1150.8600000000001, "text": " So when we have an overall picture"}, {"start": 1150.8600000000001, "end": 1152.8600000000001, "text": " we see from the perspective of soul"}, {"start": 1152.8600000000001, "end": 1154.8600000000001, "text": " the soul is eternal"}, {"start": 1154.8600000000001, "end": 1156.8600000000001, "text": " and then when we have the overall perspective"}, {"start": 1156.8600000000001, "end": 1158.8600000000001, "text": " then death comes, old age comes"}, {"start": 1158.8600000000001, "end": 1160.8600000000001, "text": " disease comes"}, {"start": 1160.8600000000001, "end": 1162.8600000000001, "text": " it doesn't bother a person."}, {"start": 1166.8600000000001, "end": 1168.8600000000001, "text": " Because he knows that it is a small phase"}, {"start": 1168.8600000000001, "end": 1170.8600000000001, "text": " in our eternal existence."}, {"start": 1170.8600000000001, "end": 1172.8600000000001, "text": " He gets another body"}, {"start": 1172.8600000000001, "end": 1174.8600000000001, "text": " and he works towards"}, {"start": 1174.8600000000001, "end": 1176.8600000000001, "text": " the ultimate goal."}, {"start": 1176.8600000000001, "end": 1178.8600000000001, "text": " While he is engaged in his worldly duties"}, {"start": 1178.8600000000001, "end": 1180.8600000000001, "text": " he tries cultivating"}, {"start": 1180.8600000000001, "end": 1182.8600000000001, "text": " his remembrance of God."}, {"start": 1184.8600000000001, "end": 1186.8600000000001, "text": " Is that okay?"}, {"start": 1186.8600000000001, "end": 1188.8600000000001, "text": " Everyone?"}, {"start": 1190.8600000000001, "end": 1192.8600000000001, "text": " Everyone is calm now."}, {"start": 1192.8600000000001, "end": 1194.8600000000001, "text": " Yes."}, {"start": 1194.8600000000001, "end": 1196.8600000000001, "text": " Those who are having"}, {"start": 1196.8600000000001, "end": 1198.8600000000001, "text": " for going to spiritual world"}, {"start": 1198.8600000000001, "end": 1200.8600000000001, "text": " that means they are all"}, {"start": 1200.8600000000001, "end": 1202.8600000000001, "text": " self-realized persons."}, {"start": 1202.8600000000001, "end": 1204.8600000000001, "text": " Yes."}, {"start": 1204.8600000000001, "end": 1206.8600000000001, "text": " That means all self-realized persons"}, {"start": 1206.8600000000001, "end": 1208.8600000000001, "text": " are qualified for spiritual life."}, {"start": 1208.8600000000001, "end": 1210.8600000000001, "text": " Self-realized person, genuine self-realized person"}, {"start": 1210.8600000000001, "end": 1212.8600000000001, "text": " pure devotees of the Lord, yes"}, {"start": 1212.8600000000001, "end": 1214.8600000000001, "text": " they are qualified."}, {"start": 1214.8600000000001, "end": 1216.8600000000001, "text": " And mind you self-realized"}, {"start": 1216.8600000000001, "end": 1218.8600000000001, "text": " is a very loose term."}, {"start": 1218.8600000000001, "end": 1220.8600000000001, "text": " Those who are"}, {"start": 1220.8600000000001, "end": 1222.8600000000001, "text": " genuinely self-realized"}, {"start": 1222.8600000000001, "end": 1224.8600000000001, "text": " genuine devotees of the Lord"}, {"start": 1224.8600000000001, "end": 1226.8600000000001, "text": " they may be still in the material world"}, {"start": 1226.8600000000001, "end": 1228.8600000000001, "text": " for what? For what?"}, {"start": 1228.8600000000001, "end": 1230.8600000000001, "text": " For"}, {"start": 1230.8600000000001, "end": 1232.8600000000001, "text": " representing the mission of the Lord."}, {"start": 1232.8600000000001, "end": 1234.8600000000001, "text": " For giving this knowledge to"}, {"start": 1234.8600000000001, "end": 1236.8600000000001, "text": " other Jivas in this material world"}, {"start": 1236.8600000000001, "end": 1238.8600000000001, "text": " as messengers of God."}, {"start": 1238.8600000000001, "end": 1240.8600000000001, "text": " As representative of God."}, {"start": 1240.8600000000001, "end": 1242.8600000000001, "text": " Is it clear?"}, {"start": 1242.8600000000001, "end": 1244.8600000000001, "text": " Anything else?"}, {"start": 1244.8600000000001, "end": 1246.8600000000001, "text": " Yes, Anoopji."}, {"start": 1246.8600000000001, "end": 1248.8600000000001, "text": " This is not"}, {"start": 1248.8600000000001, "end": 1250.8600000000001, "text": " but I have been reading the words"}, {"start": 1250.8600000000001, "end": 1252.8600000000001, "text": " impersonalist and personalist."}, {"start": 1252.8600000000001, "end": 1254.8600000000001, "text": " Yes."}, {"start": 1254.8600000000001, "end": 1256.8600000000001, "text": " Identity and individual."}, {"start": 1256.8600000000001, "end": 1258.8600000000001, "text": " Yes."}, {"start": 1258.8600000000001, "end": 1260.8600000000001, "text": " What is impersonalist?"}, {"start": 1260.8600000000001, "end": 1262.8600000000001, "text": " Impersonalist means"}, {"start": 1262.8600000000001, "end": 1264.8600000000001, "text": " what's the difference between"}, {"start": 1264.8600000000001, "end": 1266.8600000000001, "text": " personalist and impersonalist?"}, {"start": 1266.8600000000001, "end": 1268.8600000000001, "text": " Impersonalist means who say that"}, {"start": 1268.8600000000001, "end": 1270.8600000000001, "text": " ultimate absolute truth or God is impersonal."}, {"start": 1270.8600000000001, "end": 1272.8600000000001, "text": " Impersonal means"}, {"start": 1272.8600000000001, "end": 1274.8600000000001, "text": " it's not a person."}, {"start": 1274.8600000000001, "end": 1276.8600000000001, "text": " Ultimate absolute truth is"}, {"start": 1276.8600000000001, "end": 1278.8600000000001, "text": " impersonal."}, {"start": 1278.8600000000001, "end": 1280.8600000000001, "text": " Impersonal means he is some energy."}, {"start": 1282.8600000000001, "end": 1284.8600000000001, "text": " The ultimate reality"}, {"start": 1284.8600000000001, "end": 1286.8600000000001, "text": " is after moksha"}, {"start": 1286.8600000000001, "end": 1288.8600000000001, "text": " we that spirit soul become"}, {"start": 1288.8600000000001, "end": 1290.8600000000001, "text": " of that infinite universe"}, {"start": 1290.8600000000001, "end": 1292.8600000000001, "text": " with innumerable specs of light"}, {"start": 1292.8600000000001, "end": 1294.8600000000001, "text": " and we become one point of light."}, {"start": 1294.8600000000001, "end": 1296.8600000000001, "text": " Is that very interesting?"}, {"start": 1300.8600000000001, "end": 1302.8600000000001, "text": " For us to"}, {"start": 1302.8600000000001, "end": 1304.8600000000001, "text": " aim for, to become a point of"}, {"start": 1304.8600000000001, "end": 1306.8600000000001, "text": " light in some"}, {"start": 1306.8600000000001, "end": 1308.8600000000001, "text": " vast sky with lot"}, {"start": 1308.8600000000001, "end": 1310.8600000000001, "text": " of spirits embedded in that"}, {"start": 1310.8600000000001, "end": 1312.8600000000001, "text": " sky."}, {"start": 1312.8600000000001, "end": 1314.8600000000001, "text": " So they are impersonalist."}, {"start": 1314.8600000000001, "end": 1316.8600000000001, "text": " Personalist are who believe"}, {"start": 1316.8600000000001, "end": 1318.8600000000001, "text": " that ultimately the supreme"}, {"start": 1318.8600000000001, "end": 1320.8600000000001, "text": " absolute truth is the"}, {"start": 1320.8600000000001, "end": 1322.8600000000001, "text": " personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 1322.8600000000001, "end": 1324.8600000000001, "text": " He is a person."}, {"start": 1324.8600000000001, "end": 1326.8600000000001, "text": " Now why do people"}, {"start": 1326.8600000000001, "end": 1328.8600000000001, "text": " come to impersonal conclusions"}, {"start": 1328.8600000000001, "end": 1330.8600000000001, "text": " if we use extrapolation"}, {"start": 1330.8600000000001, "end": 1332.8600000000001, "text": " and we use speculation"}, {"start": 1332.8600000000001, "end": 1334.8600000000001, "text": " if we do our own"}, {"start": 1334.8600000000001, "end": 1336.8600000000001, "text": " word jugglery to get into"}, {"start": 1336.8600000000001, "end": 1338.8600000000001, "text": " the understanding of supreme we can"}, {"start": 1338.8600000000001, "end": 1340.8600000000001, "text": " think of"}, {"start": 1340.8600000000001, "end": 1342.8600000000001, "text": " an impersonal God."}, {"start": 1342.8600000000001, "end": 1344.8600000000001, "text": " Because"}, {"start": 1344.8600000000001, "end": 1346.8600000000001, "text": " a person is limited"}, {"start": 1346.8600000000001, "end": 1348.8600000000001, "text": " by time and space."}, {"start": 1348.8600000000001, "end": 1350.8600000000001, "text": " If I give example if you are here today"}, {"start": 1350.8600000000001, "end": 1352.8600000000001, "text": " I see you I meet you I can very"}, {"start": 1352.8600000000001, "end": 1354.8600000000001, "text": " confidently say that you were not in"}, {"start": 1354.8600000000001, "end": 1356.8600000000001, "text": " Delhi."}, {"start": 1356.8600000000001, "end": 1358.8600000000001, "text": " Because you are limited by time"}, {"start": 1358.8600000000001, "end": 1360.8600000000001, "text": " and space. If you are here you are not in Delhi."}, {"start": 1360.8600000000001, "end": 1362.8600000000001, "text": " So because God is all"}, {"start": 1362.8600000000001, "end": 1364.8600000000001, "text": " pervading"}, {"start": 1364.8600000000001, "end": 1366.8600000000001, "text": " and God is present"}, {"start": 1366.8600000000001, "end": 1368.8600000000001, "text": " everywhere hence he cannot be a"}, {"start": 1368.8600000000001, "end": 1370.8600000000001, "text": " person."}, {"start": 1370.8600000000001, "end": 1372.8600000000001, "text": " And every"}, {"start": 1372.8600000000001, "end": 1374.8600000000001, "text": " person we have seen the experience"}, {"start": 1374.8600000000001, "end": 1376.8600000000001, "text": " what we have that person"}, {"start": 1376.8600000000001, "end": 1378.8600000000001, "text": " has a body which decays decomposes"}, {"start": 1378.8600000000001, "end": 1380.8600000000001, "text": " dies diseases janma"}, {"start": 1380.8600000000001, "end": 1382.8600000000001, "text": " mrityu jara viyadi and God"}, {"start": 1382.8600000000001, "end": 1384.8600000000001, "text": " is transcendental and hence"}, {"start": 1384.8600000000001, "end": 1386.8600000000001, "text": " God is not a person."}, {"start": 1388.8600000000001, "end": 1390.8600000000001, "text": " So this is using our own"}, {"start": 1390.8600000000001, "end": 1392.8600000000001, "text": " logic to get to"}, {"start": 1392.8600000000001, "end": 1394.8600000000001, "text": " understanding of who God is."}, {"start": 1394.8600000000001, "end": 1396.8600000000001, "text": " Where is Krishna"}, {"start": 1396.8600000000001, "end": 1398.8600000000001, "text": " himself?"}, {"start": 1404.8600000000001, "end": 1406.8600000000001, "text": " Moodha fools deride me when I"}, {"start": 1406.8600000000001, "end": 1408.8600000000001, "text": " understand in a human like form."}, {"start": 1408.8600000000001, "end": 1410.8600000000001, "text": " Eeshwaraha"}, {"start": 1410.8600000000001, "end": 1412.8600000000001, "text": " paramaha krishna"}, {"start": 1412.8600000000001, "end": 1414.8600000000001, "text": " sat chit ananda"}, {"start": 1414.8600000000001, "end": 1416.8600000000001, "text": " vigraha. His vigraha his form is"}, {"start": 1416.8600000000001, "end": 1418.8600000000001, "text": " he has a form"}, {"start": 1418.8600000000001, "end": 1420.8600000000001, "text": " he is a person but his vigraha"}, {"start": 1420.8600000000001, "end": 1422.8600000000001, "text": " is not a material vigraha"}, {"start": 1422.8600000000001, "end": 1424.8600000000001, "text": " is not a material form it is"}, {"start": 1424.8600000000001, "end": 1426.8600000000001, "text": " sat chit ananda vigraha."}, {"start": 1436.8600000000001, "end": 1438.8600000000001, "text": " So symbol of Islam there."}, {"start": 1438.8600000000001, "end": 1440.8600000000001, "text": " So idol of Islam I"}, {"start": 1440.8600000000001, "end": 1442.8600000000001, "text": " have别 tenga"}, {"start": 1442.8600000000001, "end": 1446.8600000000001, "text": " oats"}, {"start": 1446.8600000000001, "end": 1448.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1448.8600000000001, "end": 1450.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1454.8600000000001, "end": 1456.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1456.8600000000001, "end": 1460.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1460.8600000000001, "end": 1462.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1462.8600000000001, "end": 1464.8600000000001, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1464.8600000000001, "end": 1466.8600000000001, "text": " and"}]}